<author>ktạbyẗ, rw̉wf ṣdqy</author>
<title>yạ rb lạ tnsạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạ rb lạ tnsạny lạ tḥjb wjhk ʿny ạjʿl hmwmạaⁿ wḥznạaⁿ fy qlby
 yqwl ʿdwy ạrtfʿt ʿlyh yqwl ạ̉ny qd tzʿzʿt
 ạ̉mạ ạ̉nạ ʿly̱ rḥmtk qd twklt bkẖlạṣk ybthj qlby
 (ạ̉gẖny llrb ạ̉gẖny llrb lạ̉nh ạ̉ḥsn ạ̹ly̱)2
 wjhk yạ rb ạ̉ṭlb lạ tḥjb wjhk ʿny
 qd knt ʿwny flạ trfḍny wlạ ttrkny ạ̉gẖny llrb
 (ạ̉gẖny llrb ạ̉gẖny llrb lạ̉nh ạ̉ḥsn ạ̹ly̱)2</lyrics>
</song>